                <div id="p1" class="page" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
                    <p>I was just sitting here thinking about how lucky I am to have you in my life. ‚ú®</p>
                    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); changePage(1)">Read On üåø</button>
                </div>

                <div id="p2" class="page" style="display: none; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
                    <p>Thank you for always being there, for the laughs, and for being such an amazing soul!</p>
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px; justify-content: center;">
                        <button class="nav-btn" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); stickerExplosion(event)">Send High-Five üôå</button>
                        <button class="nav-btn" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); changePage(1)">More ‚òï</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="p3" class="page" style="display: none; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
                    <p>You're the best! Can't wait for our next adventure. <br><b>Cheers to you! ü•Ç</b></p>
                    <button onclick="event.stopPropagation(); resetAll()" style="background:none; border:none; text-decoration:underline; color:#81b29a; cursor:pointer; font-size: 0.75rem;">Close Letter</button>
                </div>
